    "en": {
      "name": "Legendary Klesha Six Samurai - Shi En",
      "effect": "1 Warrior Tuner + 1+ non-Tuner \"Six Samurai\" monsters\nIf this card is Synchro Summoned: You can add 1 \"Six Samurai\" monster or \"Shien\" Effect Monster from your Deck or GY to your hand. You can only use this effect of \"Legendary Klesha Six Samurai - Shi En\" once per turn. Once per turn, when your opponent activates a monster effect (Quick Effect): You can negate the activation, and if you do, destroy that monster. If this card on the field would be destroyed by battle or card effect, you can destroy 1 other monster you control instead.",
      "official": false
    },
